WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.280
Right, Ms. Campo?

00:00:00.407 --> 00:00:01.396
Yes.

00:00:01.571 --> 00:00:03.405
What was on the napkin?

00:00:04.605 --> 00:00:06.483
My name and address.

00:00:07.106 --> 00:00:08.471
And your price?

00:00:09.657 --> 00:00:11.348
Yes, $400.

00:00:12.340 --> 00:00:13.418
It's a hard line of work.

00:00:13.969 --> 00:00:15.546
Yes, and dangerous.

00:00:16.179 --> 00:00:18.090
In fact, haven't you told
your friends many times...

